{"tid":1157483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1952 年上海被送終，2019 年到香港","createTime":"2019-05-16T10:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T11:13:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0ca0e545f6eebc5e6710731033a665c73782d9d9","tid":1157483,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:25:06.000Z","msg":"1949 年大陸赤化後，被中共統戰時吹捧為民族資本家的商人的好日子過了不久，便兔死狗烹。1952 年，中共搞「五反 &mdash; 反行賄、反偷稅漏稅、反偷工減料、反盜騙國家財產、反盜竊國家經濟情報」，把上海的資本家以經濟罪行的名義鬥到七彩，八百多個資本家跳樓收場，當時的上海市長陳毅形容他們是「空降部隊」。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼要跳樓？因為資本家被中共以逃稅等罪名拘捕和充公財產之後，還要被酷刑對待，屈打成招，最後頂不順的就自殺收場。他們選擇跳樓，是因為跳樓人人都看到，不會被指控逃跑，不會連累家人。<br />\n<br />\n1952 年，上海有八百多個空降部隊跳樓，2019 年香港，講到明送中條例下，中共可要求特區政府凍結沒收任何人在香港的財產，然後送上大陸受審。<br />\n<br />\n這對香港的資本家和外國企業來說，根本就是 1952 年上海模式的警號，中共隨時可以製造證據，然後要港府搞你。這時候，香港等於和大陸屬同一個司法區域，那時候《香港政策法》的獨立關稅地位也玩完了。<br />\n<br />\n到槍聲響了才逃跑實在太遲了吧，大批資本家和企業高層撤資、搬辦事處、走佬，到時香港正式死亡，攬炒，very good。<br />\n<br />\n林勉一<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/0_0VOPA_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F0_0VOPA_1200x0.png&h=19f4ed83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/1952-年上海被送終-2019-年到香港/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F1952-%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%81%E7%B5%82-2019-%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%B0%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%2F&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdfz11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=42895f73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F1952-%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%81%E7%B5%82-2019-%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%B0%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%2F&h=52b0e36b\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/1952-年上海被送終-2019-年到香港/</a>"},{"pid":"fd8f9048656923a27a7c73417ede0892d1d27804","tid":1157483,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:32:15.000Z","msg":"呢個比喻非常貼切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f02226c238fe9820e321a544f32e2500c6a0ab","tid":1157483,"uid":49197,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:34:39.000Z","msg":"當時的上海市長陳毅形容他們是「空降部隊」。<br />\n<br />\n呢條打靶咁講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c848f6c7569bfbb7f84329ca271ac8634a06c902","tid":1157483,"uid":49197,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:42:22.000Z","msg":"所謂&ldquo;反偷稅漏稅&rdquo;是從<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光緒年間上海開埠算起</span></strong></span>，資本家傾家蕩產也交不起&ldquo;稅&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n原來中共一早就有鋪[修例追溯]既癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae8e2c467a0cbcd77881d4cee0b4846f5fdd2c5","tid":1157483,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d4f02226c238fe9820e321a544f32e2500c6a0ab","tid":1157483,"uid":49197,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:34:39.000Z","msg":"當時的上海市長陳毅形容他們是「空降部隊」。<br />\n<br />\n呢條打靶咁講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:50:39.000Z","msg":"這就是中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c030d696c55c7a4158d574e64496402119e17ed0","tid":1157483,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:52:20.000Z","msg":"等睇死廢老話:你又唔係有錢佬 又唔係罪犯怕乜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451f31e36c7792b780f1c32514de5c570aba6bef","tid":1157483,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5fea9a65ff3d2fa2a6275cbee89f5c4d6f90a8","tid":1157483,"uid":61748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05